body:
for the twitter account @sunofseldo, which warmly charts the micro milestones on the road to spring, such as today’s entry, which read:

“WOO! It's the milestone you've been waiting for: today the sun set at 6pm! That hasn't happened since the clocks changed back in November! And as a bonus, sunrise also moved back to 6.45am.”

to know that if we manage to keep going, the season will change, a landslide of light

